OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FA teenage boy has been acquitted of
OL,7,Fthe murder and manslaughter of a nine-
OL,8,Fyear-old girl who died from a fatal
OL,9,Fstab wound.
OL,11,FThe 16-year-old, who cannot be
OL,12,Fidentified due to his age, was cleared
OL,13,Fof both charges by a jury at Bristol
OL,14,FCrown Court on Thursday.
OL,16,FAria Thorpe died after sustaining a
OL,17,Fknife wound to her chest at her home
OL,18,Fin Weston-super-Mare, North Somerset,
OL,19,Fon December 15 last year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
