FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FShe was described by her family as
OL,7,F"the most beautiful little soul `
OL,8,Fhappy-go-lucky, full of light, and
OL,9,Fjoy".
OL,11,FAfter the incident, the boy left
OL,12,FAria's home and went to a nearby
OL,13,Frailway station ` where he told a
OL,14,Fgroup of children that her death was
OL,15,Fan "accident".
OL,26,@wD@DOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FHe later told the jury at Bristol
OL,7,FCrown Court that he had picked up a
OL,8,Fknife from the kitchen of Aria's home
OL,9,Fand went into the lounge, where she
OL,10,Fwas sitting on the sofa, to "scare"
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,FThe boy demonstrated moving the knife
OL,14,Fin a ninja-style way before jabbing it
OL,15,Ftowards Aria as if he was fencing. He
OL,16,Fsaid the knife accidentally went into
OL,17,FAria, causing the fatal injury.
OL,26,@rD@]OUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FJurors returned the verdicts of not
OL,7,Fguilty to both charges. After they
OL,8,Fwere returned, several members of the
OL,9,Fpublic gallery left the court room
OL,10,Fquietly.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, the boy said he had
OL,13,Fwanted to "scare" Aria and picked up
OL,14,Fthe knife, which had a 21cm blade,
OL,15,Ffrom near the kitchen sink before
OL,16,Fgoing into the lounge.
OL,26,@uD@KOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FHe told the jury: "Aria stood up and I
OL,7,Fwas waving around the knife. Then at
OL,8,Fsome point I decided that I was going
OL,9,Fto try to make her flinch and scare
OL,10,Fher, to get a reaction.
OL,12,F"I leaned forward, acted like I was
OL,13,Ffencing."
OL,15,FThe defendant said Aria had been in
OL,16,Ffront of him at the time.
OL,18,F"She had almost taken a step forward
OL,19,Fbut without taking a step forward
OL,20,Fbecause before she could, it
OL,21,Fhappened," he said.
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOUuD@IO]zD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,F"I don't know what she was doing. The
OL,7,Fknife went into her. Then I pulled it
OL,8,Fout. I didn't know what to do. She put
OL,9,Fher hand to her chest."
OL,11,FThe boy said Aria then fell to the
OL,12,Ffloor on her front. "I thought she had
OL,13,Fdied," he told the court.
OL,15,F"I got scared, I panicked. So I ran to
OL,16,Fthe kitchen with the knife and I put
OL,17,Fit back into the sink."
OL,19,FHe did not check on Aria after she was
OL,20,Finjured, did not raise the alarm with
OL,21,Fneighbours or ring for an ambulance.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]tD@UOUuD@FO]wD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
