OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FThe court heard the boy walked to
OL,7,FWorle railway station, where he told a
OL,8,Fgroup of children that he had killed
OL,9,FAria accidentally.
OL,11,FHis mobile phone had been previously
OL,12,Fbeen confiscated by his mother and he
OL,13,Fborrowed the phone of a boy at the
OL,14,Fstation.
OL,16,FHe then searched for "what happens if
OL,17,Fyou kill...".
OL,19,FA girl at the train station rang
OL,20,Fpolice on 999 to report what the boy
OL,21,Fhad said and police quickly attended.
OL,26,@xD@VOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FThe boy ran onto a train, which police
OL,7,Fstopped from departing the station. He
OL,8,Fwas then arrested.
OL,10,FWhen asked how he was feeling about
OL,11,Fwhat happened at that time, the boy
OL,12,Freplied: "I felt horrible".
OL,14,FHome Office pathologist Dr Amanda
OL,15,FJeffery found Aria died from a single
OL,16,Fstab wound, which went through her
OL,17,Fheart.
OL,26,@tD@JOUtD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FDr Jeffery told the jury that Aria
OL,7,Fwould have died "very swiftly" from
OL,8,Fthe injury, which was between 7.5 and
OL,9,F8cm deep.
OL,11,FAria attended school on the day of her
OL,12,Fdeath and was collected from an after-
OL,13,Fschool dance class by her mother, Tori
OL,14,FHull, at about 4.30pm.
OL,16,FThey went shopping for mini-pizzas and
OL,17,Ftoppings, which they made together. Ms
OL,18,FHull left for an evening work shift
OL,19,Fshortly after, with Aria watching
OL,20,FYouTube videos on the television.
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
