OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782652703
OL,3,CTeenage boy cleared of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe
OL,6,FFamily friend Ollie Sheppard, who was
OL,7,Fstaying temporarily at the house,
OL,8,Freturned there after work at about 6pm.
OL,10,FHe found Aria on the floor of the
OL,11,Fliving room and rang 999, with police
OL,12,Fand paramedics arriving a short time
OL,13,Flater.
OL,15,FAria could not be saved and was
OL,16,Fpronounced dead at 6.58pm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
